          <div style="border:1px solid #dbeafe;border-radius:10px;padding:10px;margin:8px 0;">
            <h3 style="margin:0 0 6px 0;color:#1d4ed8;">Quick practical steps</h3>
            <p style="margin:0;line-height:1.6;">Read Lesson 1: What is Python? to understand the language purpose and uses. Type the example: print("Welcome to the Python course!") in a text editor or interactive prompt. To run code on your machine, follow Lesson 2: Installing Python for download/installation and verification. Next study step: proceed to Lesson 3: Variables and Data Types to learn how to store and use data.</p>
          </div>
        
          <div style="border:1px solid #dbeafe;border-radius:10px;padding:10px;margin:8px 0;">
